overview: Everyone loves rapping along and learning multiplication with D.J. Doc Roc, the Hip Hop Hamster. Positive lyrics, fun music, and high-energy action make these multiplication rap songs irresistible. Multiplication facts through 12 are easy to learn and remember with a different song for each set of rap facts. Also includes an informative "What is Multiplication" section and skip counting songs.
title: Multiplication Rap
